WingRazor followed Windlord as Rave Transformed and stood watch on 
the hull of the ship. "Dont worry Guys, Remember were the good guys, 
we always win in the end."

WingRazor smiled. "Take care kiddo." She turned transforming into her 
Eagle form and took off. 
***************************

Meanwhile The stasis pods cooled... The one nearest the maximal's 
base became active and began healing the protoform within. 

The one nearest the Pred bases lay quite... a blinking light flash 
two symbols... Maxi, and pred. As the computer began to prep the bot 
for revival all it needed was an activation code...
